{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:d","text":"double","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, ","type":"text"},{"text":"1","type":"text"},{"text":"⁄","type":"text"},{"text":"16","type":"text"},{"text":" of the world, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so on.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"type":"text","text":" method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"zoomLevel","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1026","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The zoom level of the receiver."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/zoomLevel":{"title":"zoomLevel","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapView"}]}}}